data.description: Welcome to this great townhome conveniently located in this quiet residential neighborhood. This property has so much to offer for those looking to make a space their own and secure an exceptional value. This home boasts 2 spacious bedrooms, 2 baths, tons of living space, and attached 2 car garage and easy access to the entire North Metro. Rarely do such exciting opportunities come to the market at such a reasonable price. Plan your tour of this new listing today and get ready to call this house your new home.
